lenders.name: Laura
lenders.loan_because: I want to share my fortune with needy people.  I am so fortunate to have some many daily blessings from food, a warm shower, comfortable bed and a safe warm house to live in.  Living in the US, we often forget that these luxuries are not there for many people around the world.  I just want to share my wealth in hopes to make someone else's life better!
lenders.occupational_info: I am a married 45 years old and we have 2 beautiful healthy children.  Jack who is 14 and Lucy who is 10.  We are Christians and live a happy life in Atlanta, Georgia.

lenders.name: Sara
lenders.loan_because: I care! Others need it more than I do! To set a good example!
lenders.occupational_info: Ambitious, educated and passionate. In my early 20s, don't have a lot of money, but have enough to help :)
